  "title": "A &#8216;very large quadrilateral&#8217; UFO was observed in Cruzeiro Velho-DF [1994]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/03/a-very-large-quadrilateral-ufo-was-observed-in-cruzeiro-velho-df-1994/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1ok",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUN 25th, 1994</strong>. Time: 21:10. Duration: 30 minutes. In the Cruzeiro Velho region, Distrito Federal, two people observed an unidentified flying object at high altitude flying at a slow speed from the Northeast to Southeast direction. According to the witnesses, the UFO was shaped like a &#8220;very large quadrilateral&#8221; and had the &#8220;color of fire&#8221;. The sighting took place during a clear night and was performed with the naked eye. No filming or photographs were taken of the event.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.368. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Cruzeiro Velho, Distrito Federal</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>JUN 25th, 1994. Time: 21:10. Duration: 30 minutes. In the Cruzeiro Velho region, Distrito Federal, two people observed an unidentified flying object at high altitude flying at a slow speed from the Northeast to Southeast direction. According to the witnesses, the UFO was shaped like a &#8220;very large quadrilateral&#8221; and had the &#8220;color of fire&#8221;. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
